headline: FactSet Schedules First Quarter 2025 Earnings Call
summary: NORWALK, Conn., Nov. 20, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- FactSet (NYSE: FDS | NASDAQ: FDS), a global financial digital platform and enterprise solutions provider, announced today that it will release its financial and operating results for the first quarter fiscal 2025, ending November 30, 2024, on Thursday, December 19, 2024.
